Name: amyotrophic neuralgia
Definition: A primary bacterial infectious disease that results in infection located in skin

Name: obsolete papilledema associated with decreased ocular pressure

Name: brachial plexus neuritis
Definition: A mitochondrial encephalomyopathy that is characterized by mitochondrial myopathy

Name: brachial plexus lesion

Name: obsolete nerve root and plexus disorder
